    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "What do you mean by <i>deep copy</i>? Behavior of <code>toString</code> is not explicitly defined for <code>String</code> in JLS (but it is kind of apparent, that it should return itself). However string memory manipulation is something which I would expect to be in JLS or JVM spec... and as String is immutable it would not make sense to make any copies."
