    "body" : "For the surround-with-quotation-marks part: while default <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/lang/Object.html#toString()\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Object.toString</a> really returns type information, whenever a toString can return an actual stringified value, it does not provide a type-hint."
