    "answer_id" : 43628515,
    "question_id" : 43628423,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You wouldn't find any guarantee in the JLS but you do have one in <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/String.html#toString--\" rel=\"noreferrer\">the javadoc</a>:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>This object (which is already a string!) is itself returned.</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
